parameters:
Teacher: Ah, Shark Mountain... umm... about that 250,000 yen
thing... the one they sell at the convenience store...

Memimi: No... th-that's not it! Teacher!! It's a serious
issue if the student council president is prostituting! I
understand!! But, there are circumstances...

Teacher: Ah, no... that's fine... the laws and ordinances in
Mudane City don't really function well... Today is that...
um, may I ask you for a favor...? Here, the ticket...

Memimi: What are you thinking, you lewd teacher!!? Buying a
student's body with money, have some shame!!! Even though
I'm the one selling!

Teacher: Eek... w-wait... I am still a teacher! Having
relations with a student is absolutely out of the question!!

Memimi: Eh... then why would you spend 250,000 yen for such
a ticket...

Teacher: Please... I want you to wear your usual uniform and
step on my dick while berating me!! It might be slightly
different from the intended use of the ticket... but I...
I!!

Memimi: What kind of passionate request is this guy
making...
